mods.abstract: Invoice (No. 2055) for an order placed for the Overton High Men's Club by Don Knight for 100 one color window cards for a Barbeque Supper at the Overton High Men's Club on October 29. Receipt indicates the agreed price, quantity, shipping method, and a description of the posters.
